column5: ~~~been a watchen these birds now for a few years, and yesterday the Adult female returned to the nest with a deer carcass which the eaglets torn into. also seen on the dinner table, a hawk, crow, and earlier a lot of phish. neither of these nest have any human contact, the U of Iowa is monitoring 2 nest, one is just over a trout farm
